<ns1:propertyName>{$property/propertyName/text()}</ns1:propertyName> <ns1:propertyValue>{$property/propertyValue/text()}</ns1:propertyValue> </ns1:property> } </ns1:properties> </ns:payload> </ns:E2G_importEmployees> </soap:Body> </soap:Envelope>
